name: VB.Net CSS Parser
short_description: This is one of the first .Net CSS Parsers. It is built using VB.Net on Windows XP for the .Net Framework 2.0. This was designed to overcome both IE and Firefox's shortcomings and to develop a CSS engine which can apply formatting to WinForm objects.
